Mixe them together and make an Oyntment: Into the which hee puts a Stick, dipp'd in the Blood of the wounded perſon, and dryed, and bindeth up the wound with a rowler dipt every day in the hot Vrine of the wounded perſon. For the annointing of the Weapon hee addes moreover;



                     Honey, one ounce,


                     Bulls fat, one dram.
